Dino Natali https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dino_Natali 0 Dino Domenico Natali (better known as Dino Natali) is an American actor born on September 19, 1931 in San Francisco, California, USA. He is best known for playing Officer Zatelli, the gay police officer, on the sitcom Barney Miller.He also guest-starred on two episodes The Lucy Show and Get Smart and had a small appearance in the movie Love at First Bite (1979).
